1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Start the game by configure and play

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Press the space bar to shoot the hook

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Press "D" to throw a dynamite to destroy any minerals

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Collect valuable minerals to attain the level's target and go to the next level

5
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:35,000
Gold is worth $500 and Gem $1500

6
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:42,000
The hook should swing in a pendulum

7
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:48,000
It should start rewinding when it hits the boundaries

8
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:54,000
Complete three levels to win the game

9
00:00:54,000 --> 00:01:04,000
Now is a demonstration for a failure case

10
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:14,000
The game is lost if the timer is up at any level

1
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:24,000
Recrawling a stone and missing a shot are the main losing reasons

12
00:01:24,000 --> 00:02:20,000
You may skip to the end to see what happens if the timer runs up